Kohana Notice changelog
=======================

Version 0.4.2 (15th May 2015)
-----------------------------

Maintenance release

Version 0.4.1 (27th July 2014)
------------------------------

 - Fix Composer branch alias name

Version 0.4.0 (21st July 2014)
------------------------------

 - Add Composer installation support
 - Add PSR-0 support
 - Add LICENSE file
 - Add CHANGELOG file

Version 0.3.0 (13th December 2011)
----------------------------------

 - Kill view render magic, notices are always rendered as array
 - Support lookup for a message from the message file if a message is
   prefixed with colon (:)
 - Use CSS 'class' instead of 'id' in the view

Version 0.2.0 (8th May 2011)
----------------------------

 - Major rewrite
 - Support JSON and HTML rendering
 - Support configurable session type

Version 0.1.0 (12th September 2010)
-----------------------------------

 - Initial release

